_sText:
Sorry about the screen shots being really low quality, I can't take screen shots with steam, my computer won't let me so I had to use an actual camera and upload the images to my computer. But that's also why I included a video, to make up for the crappy pics.

This map revolves around my all time favorite gun. the P90. I have been using the P90 for almost as long as I've been playing css and I was a bit dissapointed when I noticed the very low amount of maps for this gun. So I went out and studied the P90 and how well it works at different distances, using this knowledge, i made this map. This map has 4 buildings, 3 levels above the buildings, a middle tube with spiral staircases, a huge basement with plenty of structure and several other pieces of structure around the map. It is overall the best i've seen for the P90. I hope you all like it!

This map has 40 spawn points, buy zones, a skybox a .nav file and vehicles. It can also be used with other guns other than the P90, but overall, the P90 works the best here.
